00:46:24.910 --> 00:46:27.390
The only thing I'm doing is,
I'm doing a pretty good job

00:46:27.390 --> 00:46:30.070
at designing games and
learning experiences,

00:46:30.070 --> 00:46:31.470
and we're collecting data.

00:46:31.470 --> 00:46:34.890
And I'm sorry if the
guy found this title.

00:46:34.890 --> 00:46:41.280
Well, it generated a fair
amount of hate, really.

00:46:41.280 --> 00:46:43.382
We had many people
who got awareness

00:46:43.382 --> 00:46:44.340
about what we're doing.

00:46:44.340 --> 00:46:46.320
And some people were thinking,
well, that's a good thing.

00:46:46.320 --> 00:46:47.280
I want to try that.

00:46:47.280 --> 00:46:49.120
Which is good.

00:46:49.120 --> 00:46:52.090
But of course, we have
to take some perspective

00:46:52.090 --> 00:46:55.400
and some distance with
the data we're getting.

00:46:58.390 --> 00:47:04.722
Really, after one and half
hours, 95% of the kids,

00:47:04.722 --> 00:47:06.430
after having played
one and a half hours,

00:47:06.430 --> 00:47:09.740
are mastering the rules
of algebra in the game.

00:47:09.740 --> 00:47:13.320
There is some help in
the game, but it's really

00:47:13.320 --> 00:47:15.950
mathematical gameplay,
as I would call it.

00:47:15.950 --> 00:47:18.410
So that means that they
are really learning.

00:47:18.410 --> 00:47:20.320
So it's very efficient.

00:47:20.320 --> 00:47:22.450
And the data we're collecting
are really, really,

00:47:22.450 --> 00:47:25.140
really interesting for
understanding the learning

00:47:25.140 --> 00:47:26.420
process.

00:47:26.420 --> 00:47:27.590
And it's real learning.

00:47:27.590 --> 00:47:29.930
Although it's not transferred
to pencil and paper,

00:47:29.930 --> 00:47:30.950
we can do that later.

00:47:30.950 --> 00:47:35.090
And we have made many stuff to
be able to ease this process.

00:47:37.840 --> 00:47:41.490
Yeah, so I want to
say we are humble

00:47:41.490 --> 00:47:43.910
and we are really into learning.

00:47:43.910 --> 00:47:47.829
We are not interested in those
kinds of titles or headlines

00:47:47.829 --> 00:47:49.203
although it gives
some publicity.

