So as a teacher, you
know that there are

00:48:24.490 --> 00:48:26.320
big differences between kids.

00:48:26.320 --> 00:48:30.490
But now we can measure
that with adaptive levels,

00:48:30.490 --> 00:48:34.220
with math in the game mechanics,
time on task, and so on.

00:48:34.220 --> 00:48:36.590
10 times.

