If you think of
that, you say why

00:48:38.930 --> 00:48:42.180
are these kids in
the same classroom?

00:48:42.180 --> 00:48:43.760
It doesn't work like that.

00:48:43.760 --> 00:48:47.220
I mean, there is a problem,
fundamental problem, there.

00:48:47.220 --> 00:48:51.390
And not only that, we know
the number of exercises

00:48:51.390 --> 00:48:52.680
we have to give to kids.

