And between the slowest
and the fastest,

00:48:55.570 --> 00:48:58.530
seven more content,
seven more content

00:48:58.530 --> 00:49:01.700
we have to deliver
to the slowest kids.

00:49:01.700 --> 00:49:04.430
So we can put a number on this.

00:49:04.430 --> 00:49:05.480
And it's not one.

00:49:05.480 --> 00:49:07.070
It's not 0.5.

00:49:07.070 --> 00:49:09.160
It's 7 and 10 times.

00:49:09.160 --> 00:49:10.555
It's really big numbers.

