For example, now in many
countries in South America,

00:50:17.090 --> 00:50:20.470
they have a one to one
with the same tablets.

00:50:20.470 --> 00:50:25.700
What can you do if in a whole
country each kid has a tablet?

00:50:25.700 --> 00:50:28.610
What kind of interaction
can you make?

00:50:28.610 --> 00:50:32.240
What kind of learning experience
can you generate there?

00:50:32.240 --> 00:50:34.840
It's fascinating, the number
of facilities we have there.

00:50:37.410 --> 00:50:40.570
I think we're going to
spend time exploring this.

00:50:40.570 --> 00:50:42.950
How can we create a
game experience there

00:50:42.950 --> 00:50:43.825
with this hardware?

00:50:46.930 --> 00:50:49.240
Much more to do
with higher math.

00:50:49.240 --> 00:50:52.405
There are many areas
of exploration.

